Angel Prime




Angel Prime smiled and laughed. "The name of Angel Prime was given to 
me by the matrix. Also I good enough to be one of the carriers of the 
maximal matrix. you are a low class warrior. I will not let you hurt 
my friend. I don't know your name and I don't care." Angel Prime flew 
forward and swung both blades at Recon.
